Package com.github.wuic

This package is the most general package of the WUIC library.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
FilesGroup This class represents a set a files associated to their Configuration.
Util This class provides conveniences static methods.
WuicFacade This class is a facade which exposes the WUIC features by simplifying them within some exposed methods.
 

Enum Summary
FileType Enumeration of the possible types to be compressed and / or aggregated in WUIC.
 

Exception Summary
WuicException This exception is an unchecked exception used for convenience reasons in the WuicFacade.
 

Package com.github.wuic Description

This package is the most general package of the WUIC library. Most of the interface and classes of WUIC are split within the sub-packages.
